Step 1:
    Trigger the zero generation alert                   |       Verify the Alert state is set to "Open"

Step 2:
    Verify an email was sent to the user                |       Verify the Alert state is still set to "Open"

Step 3:
    Login as the test user, and acknowledge the Alert   |       Verify the Alert state is set to "Acknowledged"

Step 4:
    Untrigger the zero generation alert                 |       Verify the Alert state is set to "Closed"